Grass was a plant grown during the Big Cats & WWF event as part of the lion restoration. First, grass seeds would be obtained from grasslands. At the planting area, the seeds could be planted and grow over several hours. The grass could become diseased and cured using a plant cure, and otherwise would die. After fully grown, the "Get xp" option could be used to receive 284.5 Farming experience. 7 grass had to be fully grown to complete the event.

'''Grass''' was a plant grown during the [[Big Cats & WWF]] event as part of the lion restoration. First, [[grass seed]]s would be obtained from [[Grassland (Big Cats & WWF)|grasslands]]. At the planting area, the seeds could be planted and grow over several hours. The grass could become diseased and cured using a [[plant cure]], and otherwise would die. After fully grown, the "Get xp" option could be used to receive 284.5 [[Farming]] experience. 7 grass had to be fully grown to complete the event.
